Class AbstractAgentController

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.logspace.agent.impl.AbstractAgentController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AgentController
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsoleAgentController, DummyAgentController, HqAgentController, TestAgentController

    public abstract class AbstractAgentController
extends Object
implements AgentController
    Base class for AgentControllers. Initializes the system name and handles un-/registering of Agents.
